::Feline::

She wondered what the mission is.  She walks up and stands next to 
Skulletron.  She leans over and whispers into his ear,"You'll be able 
to pull this mission off without a hitch. Don't worry, I'll back you 
up as much as you back me up."
She glided her hand up his back, over his shoudler and down his 
chest.  She looked at him as she walked over to a chair.  She swaded 
her hips as she walked. She tail swung evenly with her walk. She 
turned and sat in the chair while looking at Skulletron.  She patted 
the empty seat next to her and smiled seductively  at Skulletron.
